{"tid":1873672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實觀塘先係大撚獲","createTime":"2020-02-10T18:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T21:17:55.000Z","uid":60916,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c67d96ff9e630798de25113f9fc606167ac4bd60","tid":1873672,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:47:29.000Z","msg":"先唔講打邊爐呢單野<br />\n我諗呢單要爆都會係全港爆<br />\n觀塘幾大獲下既原因係好雜下都集齊唔少支那人<br />\n唔理商業區office定係工廠區一帶好多支那人返工<br />\n話就話依家home office姐但都仲有唔少支那人<br />\n仲有前日警署被捕手足都係有發燒<br />\n相信都係潛在患者<br />\n同埋近年好多腥香港人住觀塘<br />\n唔理公屋秀茂坪樂華定係私樓嗰邊<br />\n都比支那人逼爆哂<br />\n仲未計好多廢中老成日返大陸<br />\n<br />\n第二區會爆社區爆發我估大爆既唔會係青衣<br />\n係大西北周東涌<br />\n因為青衣應該只係煙幕都好少事<br />\n呢兩個區最多支那病毒人會過既地方"},{"pid":"f09563b8a7f541189c359a2e137f633db8eae8ee","tid":1873672,"uid":198590,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T18:47:38.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#60916 - 山齊士超級綠洲</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請保持批判性思考，善用「上一頁」和「不推文回覆」<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">該會員以往言論 (7)：</div><code>1 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eQijrT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eQijrT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>2 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eBHfvT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eBHfvT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠, 做假新聞</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/eAEteT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/eAEteT</a><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqExT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqExT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">玩膠</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/esqBmT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/esqBmT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">洗白黑警</span><br />\n<code>6 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/epmkQT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/epmkQT</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍言論</span><br />\n<code>7 .</code><a hre